43:13.324 --> 43:22.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Out back of their
classroom in
Columbia, South Carolina, 4- and
5-year-olds

43:22.366 --> 43:30.774 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
are building a fortress with
their teacher,
