43:30.808 --> 43:36.046 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Browder is that rare bird: a man
in a woman's
world of work, an early
childhood teacher

43:36.080 --> 43:42.119 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in a profession that's been a
measly 2 to
5 percent male for years, is
desperately looking

43:42.152 --> 43:44.388 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to up the percentage.

43:44.421 --> 43:52.363 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
