industry have
gone poof, 5.7 million since
2000 in manufacturing

43:52.396 --> 43:59.003 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
alone, that de-industrialization
has become
a stock explanation for Rust
Belt resentment,

43:59.036 --> 44:00.738 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
