44:07.778 --> 44:13.550 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: And, in fact, the
share of working
men ages 25 to 54 has fallen
dramatically

44:13.584 --> 44:19.289 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
