services.

44:38.042 --> 44:41.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So we're more than making up for
the jobs
we're losing, but the
characteristics of those

44:41.912 --> 44:47.618 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
jobs, the identity associated
with a worker
who holds one of those jobs, the
pay associated

44:47.651 --> 44:49.386 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
