and loved for
13 years.

45:01.165 --> 45:06.870 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So I asked him, why don't more
men go into
this profession?

45:06.904 --> 45:12.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMIE BROWDER, Teacher: I think
it's a lack
of information, a lack of
understanding how

45:12.776 --> 45:20.117 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
