children's lives,
a lack of understanding what you
mean to a

45:20.150 --> 45:22.019 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
community.

45:22.052 --> 45:26.190 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: So, men see jobs
like grade school
teaching as low status, low
upward mobility.

45:26.223 --> 45:30.961 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMIE BROWDER: It's almost like,
if you enter
the classroom, this is where you
will be,

45:30.994 --> 45:32.796 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and this is where you will spend
the rest
of your life.

45:32.830 --> 45:34.164 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: You're stuck.

45:34.198 --> 45:38.235 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMIE BROWDER: You're stuck, and
this is the
set, scheduled pay.

45:38.268 --> 45:44.708 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So you will only be able to move
yourself
up through additional education,
which requires

45:44.742 --> 45:49.680 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
money, and then also by just
each additional
year.

45:49.713 --> 45:53.584 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: So, you can't have
a fantasy
about striking it rich, you
mean?

45:53.617 --> 45:55.018 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JAMIE BROWDER: No, no, no.

45:55.052 --> 45:58.489 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I think that's almost
somewhat anti-American.

45:58.522 --> 46:03.060 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: Professor
Stevenson's answer
is more gender-specific.

46:03.093 --> 46:12.236 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BETSEY STEVENSON: I think they
feel stigmatized,
like they're going in to do
girls' work.

46:12.269 --> 46:13.270 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
These are jobs.

46:13.303 --> 46:15.038 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
They're good jobs.

46:15.072 --> 46:20.344 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But at the same time, we need to
recognize
that there are a lot of guys who
feel, either

46:20.377 --> 46:23.447 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
