doing something
girly.

46:27.718 --> 46:30.988 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that feeling is a barrier
for them.

46:31.021 --> 46:34.091 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: S.O., you know what
that says?

46:34.124 --> 46:35.592 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
CHILD: So.

46:35.626 --> 46:37.828 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: Excellent.

46:37.861 --> 46:39.396 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Terrific reading there.

46:39.429 --> 46:41.765 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Now, not all men feel this way.

46:41.799 --> 46:43.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I once taught kindergarten.

46:43.467 --> 46:47.704 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
