a key asset for fellow teachers.

46:52.543 --> 46:56.046 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMIE BROWDER: Because I think
you offer a
different perspective.

46:56.079 --> 47:01.685 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They want to see what a man
would say, because
there's a lack of men in that
particular school,

47:01.718 --> 47:03.020 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
