47:03.053 --> 47:04.755 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So, how do you see this?

47:04.788 --> 47:06.423 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What should I do in these
situations?

47:06.456 --> 47:11.061 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: A different
perspective, what
diversity so often brings to the
table.

47:11.094 --> 47:16.967 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Also, as a male in the
classroom, Browder
gets to be a gender role model
for boys at

47:17.000 --> 47:18.802 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
