47:18.836 --> 47:21.872 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMIE BROWDER: Very few times I
can remember
when there was actually a female
student brought

47:21.905 --> 47:24.174 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to me and said, they need a role
model.

47:24.208 --> 47:27.344 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: But, with Browder,
