silly proposition.

47:48.465 --> 47:53.904 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Look, says labor
economist Teresa
Ghilarducci, the stigma of
women's work has

47:53.937 --> 47:56.006 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
