their connections
to their families.

54:04.975 --> 54:12.649 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Maybe I will have a stutter for
my whole life,
but, regardless, I'm able to
accept it because

54:12.682 --> 54:18.255 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
