home for yourself
in your work, regardless of how
many times

54:18.288 --> 54:23.994 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
your identity has been split,
whether it's
by immigration or a speech
impediment.

54:24.027 --> 54:30.567 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
My name is Jess X. Snow, and
this is my Brief
But Spectacular take on why
migration is natural.

